  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.netty.channel.ChannelHandler, io.netty.channel.ChannelInboundHandler, io.netty.channel.ChannelOutboundHandler

    @ChannelHandler.Sharable
public class FtpDataTypeCodec
extends io.netty.handler.codec.MessageToMessageCodec<org.waarp.common.file.DataBlock,org.waarp.common.file.DataBlock>
    Second CODEC :
    - encode/decode : takes a DataBlock and transforms it to a new DataBlock according to the types
    Force ASCII, EBCDIC or IMAGE (with NON PRINT). LOCAL and other subtypes are not implemented.
    Author:
    Frederic Bregier
